Author: Hamilqueer
Text: You’ve got this! What I have to do sometimes is literally refuse to open up the snack cabinet when I know my fave goodies are there just pretend the break room doesn’t even exist and don’t even enter it if possible.

Author: ijustreallymissmydog
Text: you can do it!! just because the food is there doesn’t mean you HAVE to eat it! let there be more for others and enjoy what you had planned for the day
